source: Add to every role except the selected ones
Add to the selected roles only
Allows your site to be tracked by HubSpot Analytics by adding a Javascript tracking code to every page.
Every page except the listed pages
If none of the roles are selected, all users will be tracked. If a user has any of the roles checked, that user will be tracked (or excluded, depending on the setting above).
Perform maintenance tasks for HubSpot Analytics.

Specify pages by using their paths. Enter one path per line. The '*' character is a wildcard. Example paths are %blog for the blog page and %blog-wildcard for every personal blog. %front is the front page.
target: Spécifier les pages en utilisant leurs chemins. Saisir un chemin par ligne. Le caractère «*» est un caractère de remplacement (aussi appelé joker ou wildcard). Exemples de chemins : %blog pour la page du blog et %blog-wildcard pour tous les blogs personnels. %front représente la page d’accueil.
